TextEng: Could I ask you some questions?
Me want ask questions.
Goodbye.
What's going on in this city?
Text: 이 도시에서 무슨 일이 벌어지고 있나요?

TextEng: What happen in city?
Why are you so frightened? I said I wouldn't hurt you.
Text: 왜 그렇게 겁먹은 거예요? 해치지 않겠다고 했잖아요.

TextEng: Why you so scared? Me say me not hurt you.
Text: 왜 그렇게 무서워해? 나 안 다치게 한다고 했어.

TextEng: Can I ask you some directions?
Me need directions.
Where is the nearest inn?
Where is the nearest temple?
Is there a place to buy equipment nearby?
Text: 근처에 장비를 살 수 있는 곳이 있나요?

TextEng: What's around here?
Me look for place to sleep.
Me look for temple.
Me need place to buy stuff.
What around?
Actually, I'd rather ask you about something else.
No, me have other question.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I am an adventurer looking for information; I don't mean any harm.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 전 정보를 찾는 모험가예요. 해칠 생각은 없어요.

TextEng: Get out of my way! I'll take whatever I want!
Text: 비켜! 내가 원하는 건 뭐든 가져갈 거야!

TextEng: I was just leaving.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me adventurer. Mean no harm, only look for information.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 모험가야. 해칠 생각 없어, 정보만 찾아.

TextEng: You get out of way! Me take what I wants!!
Text: 너 비켜! 나 내가 원하는 거 다 가져갈 거야!!

TextEng: Me was just going.
Tell me about these High Captains.
Tell me 'bout High Captains.
Is there nobody to stop all this?
Text: 이 모든 걸 막을 사람은 아무도 없나요?

TextEng: There nobody to stops it?
What wizards?
